descript.abstract: Contains ward boundaries within the Region of Peel (2010-2014). Municipal elections are levied at the Ward level; councillors are elected from each ward to form Municipal and Regional councils.
descript.purpose: To delineate the current municipal wards in the Region, each of which serves as a geopolitical boundary which may be used for analysis purposes and for municipal election/governance purposes.
descript.supplinf: Municipal elections were held on October 25, 2010.

idinfo.accconst: Read Only access on the V:\ drive.
idinfo.useconst: Modifications can only be made to a copy version. All modifications of original data to be completed by the area municipalities within the Region of Peel.
